      "widgets_values": [
        "Camera-locked Nano Banana path:\n\u2022 Original photo is used only for prompt synthesis\n\u2022 Nano Banana edits only the reposed splat render\n\u2022 The repaired output is blended back into the reposed view using the artifact mask\n\nThis tests whether Nano Banana can clean splat artifacts without snapping back toward the original camera."
